    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41084,41292,41504,41684</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Suzu&gt;</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>前にも、エトちゃんの
いなくなった時があったんだけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There was a time before where Miss Eto was missing too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その時はずいぶん、
双子ちゃんたち取り乱しててさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At that time the twins were really put in despair.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その人はおふたりにとって、
とても大切な人だったのですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The way you speak of this person, it seems she is an incredibly important person to the both of them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりのお母さん代わりで、
心の支えなんだってさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's her foster mother. She supports them in mind and soul.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうですか……とても立派で
素敵な母上様なのでしょうね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see... She sounds like a beautiful person. She must be a really wonderful mother.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>見た目はちっこい
妖精ちゃんだけどね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course she's beautiful! She's the cutest little fairy ever!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>妖……精……？
え、まさか、あの時の……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A...fairy? You don't mean at that time...I...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>前に比べるとずいぶん、
双子ちゃん落ち着いてるな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Compared to last time the twins are really taking it calmly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_067_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりとも、成長したのかもね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They've grown a lot when I wasn't looking.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
